        <head>Chasing A Shost</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>I've been on a train for all my life </l>
          <l>I've been chasing a ghost. </l>
        </lg>
        <lg Chorus="yes" number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>But there's one thing which </l>
          <l>Will never change </l>
          <l>And that's another doorway </l>
          <l>There's no other way </l>
          <l>So we're here to stay </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>Countless shooting stars for all my life </l>
          <l>Keep me hanging on. </l>
        </lg>
        <lg Chorus="yes" number="4" type="stanza">
          <l>But there's one thing which </l>
          <l>Will never change </l>
